1
00:00:01,110 --> 00:00:03,950
Hey, all you viewers out there!

2
00:00:03,950 --> 00:00:07,120
When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make 
sure to keep the room nice and bright,

3
00:00:07,120 --> 00:00:09,240
and sit back from the screen, 'kay?

4
00:00:10,720 --> 00:00:13,160
Previously on Fairy Tail:

5
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:18,670
A past comrade of Erza's, Jellal, is plotting 
to resurrect Zeref using the Tower of Heaven.

6
00:00:18,670 --> 00:00:21,380
We linked up with Sho and
other past friends of Erza's

7
00:00:21,380 --> 00:00:24,750
and somehow managed to defeat
Trinity Raven of the Assassin's Guild.

8
00:00:24,750 --> 00:00:29,110
But... Hurry, Natsu! Etherion is about to fire!

9
00:02:04,330 --> 00:02:07,140
What is your real goal?

10
00:02:09,310 --> 00:02:12,980
You haven't really completed 
the R-system, have you?

11
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:17,830
I haven't been doing nothing 
for these past 8 years.

12
00:02:17,830 --> 00:02:20,540
I researched the R-system myself.

13
00:02:20,540 --> 00:02:24,870
It's true there were no errors in the construction
or theory of the blueprints back then.

14
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:30,060
But there is something essential 
missing from the R-system.

15
00:02:30,060 --> 00:02:33,160
I told you, remember? You are the sacrifice.

16
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:35,070
A problem more basic than that.

17
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:38,850
The thing you lack is... magical power!

18
00:02:43,810 --> 00:02:46,330
A Prayer Under the Holy Light

19
00:02:49,830 --> 00:02:55,260
To activate a magical spell of this magnitude, 
you need a tremendous amount of magical energy.

20
00:02:55,260 --> 00:03:01,710
Even if you assembled every wizard on this 
continent, I'm not sure it would be enough.

21
00:03:01,710 --> 00:03:08,040
So of course there is no way an individual 
could store enough energy in this tower.

22
00:03:08,690 --> 00:03:13,750
And moreover, you know about the Council's 
attack but are not trying to escape.

23
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:17,300
What are you thinking?

24
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:20,050
Three minutes until Etherion.

25
00:03:20,050 --> 00:03:21,430
Jellal!

26
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:24,770
Your dream is already over!

27
00:03:24,770 --> 00:03:27,380
Do you simply wish to die like this?

28
00:03:28,020 --> 00:03:29,890
If that's the case, then we go together.

29
00:03:30,670 --> 00:03:34,350
I will not release this hand 
until the final moment!

30
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:37,860
Sure... That doesn't sound too bad.

31
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:42,590
My body was possessed by Zeref's spirit.

32
00:03:42,590 --> 00:03:44,870
No words will reach me.

33
00:03:45,350 --> 00:03:49,590
I'm nothing but a puppet used for 
the purpose of resurrecting Zeref.

34
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:51,510
Possessed?

35
00:03:51,510 --> 00:03:53,780
I wasn't able to save myself.

36
00:03:54,140 --> 00:03:58,090
Not friends nor anyone else could save me.

37
00:03:59,230 --> 00:04:04,430
There is no Heaven... There 
is no freedom, anywhere.

38
00:04:04,990 --> 00:04:09,230
Everything was over before it even began.

39
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:14,270
Etherion, final firing phase complete!

40
00:04:14,270 --> 00:04:16,480
Satellite Square, deploy!

41
00:04:16,820 --> 00:04:19,000
No problems with the transference lacrima!

42
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:19,980
Coordinates, locked.

43
00:04:19,980 --> 00:04:22,250
No signs of rejection from elemental merger.

44
00:04:22,250 --> 00:04:23,490
Begin countdown!

45
00:04:23,780 --> 00:04:25,100
Let us pray...

46
00:04:26,490 --> 00:04:27,780
Let us pray...

47
00:04:27,780 --> 00:04:29,140
Let us pray...

48
00:04:29,140 --> 00:04:30,340
Let us pray...

49
00:04:31,460 --> 00:04:32,650
Let us pray.

50
00:04:47,510 --> 00:04:48,940
That light!

51
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:50,150
It's Etherion!

52
00:04:51,470 --> 00:04:55,770
Natsu, Erza... Hurry up and escape...

53
00:04:56,720 --> 00:05:01,200
I knew that the R-system wouldn't 
be able to be completed.

54
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:05,210
But the spirit of Zeref wouldn't let me go.

55
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:11,740
It's too late to stop it. I'm a 
broken engine that he's driving...

56
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:15,340
Erza, you win.

57
00:05:15,340 --> 00:05:16,950
Please put an end to this.

58
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:20,850
That's why you came here, yes?

59
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:42,640
There is no point in delivering the final blow.

60
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:46,240
The Satellite Square is already deployed above.

61
00:05:47,170 --> 00:05:51,340
It's over. For me... and you...

62
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:56,160
Always the awkward one...

63
00:05:57,570 --> 00:06:00,490
You're also a sacrifice to Zeref, yes?

64
00:06:00,990 --> 00:06:04,470
This is my punishment for 
giving in to my weakness.

65
00:06:04,470 --> 00:06:09,720
My heart wasn't able to handle the 
huge gap between dreams and reality.

66
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:17,200
Didn't you have friends there to fill 
in for your weaknesses and deficiencies?

67
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:20,100
Erza...

68
00:06:20,950 --> 00:06:25,420
I am also repenting for my sin 
of not being able to save you.

69
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,390
I was...

70
00:06:31,380 --> 00:06:33,450
...saved.

71
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:42,180
Let us pray to the holy light!

72
00:06:42,180 --> 00:06:44,420
Release Etherion!

73
00:06:53,220 --> 00:06:54,170
Here it comes!

74
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:58,100
Natsu! Erza!

75
00:07:00,820 --> 00:07:02,500
This light...

76
00:07:03,510 --> 00:07:05,230
They didn't make it?

77
00:07:07,820 --> 00:07:09,190
Erza!

78
00:07:28,090 --> 00:07:29,530
It's over...

79
00:07:53,990 --> 00:07:56,540
Etherion has hit the target!

80
00:07:56,540 --> 00:07:59,120
Was it successfully destroyed? 
Hurry and confirm!

81
00:07:59,410 --> 00:08:02,400
Ethernano fusion density increasing!

82
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:04,670
Predicting extreme weather patterns!

83
00:08:06,380 --> 00:08:09,540
I wonder how many people were in that tower?

84
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:16,300
It was to stop Zeref from being resurrected. 
Their sacrifices were not in vain.

85
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:20,520
Whether or not what we did 
was the right decision,

86
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:24,310
that will not bring peace 
to the victims' families.

87
00:08:28,230 --> 00:08:30,060
No...

88
00:08:30,060 --> 00:08:32,610
Natsu... Erza...

89
00:08:48,730 --> 00:08:49,940
I'm alive?

90
00:08:54,020 --> 00:08:55,120
Jellal?

91
00:08:59,610 --> 00:09:03,070
Ethernano neutralizing around explosion center!

92
00:09:03,070 --> 00:09:05,090
W-Wait, that's...

93
00:09:05,090 --> 00:09:07,590
Fusion density dropping suddenly!

94
00:09:07,590 --> 00:09:10,600
A powerful, different magical 
energy is manifesting!

95
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,770
The gauge can't keep up!

96
00:09:11,770 --> 00:09:12,760
What is this?

97
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:14,280
Restore visual!

98
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:19,580
Crystal?

99
00:09:19,580 --> 00:09:21,660
No, it's magic crystal.

100
00:09:21,660 --> 00:09:23,280
Lacrima!

101
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:28,000
Hey, they're okay, right? 
Natsu, Erza, and Simon too?

102
00:09:35,110 --> 00:09:37,090
What the hell is going on?

103
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:42,570
Etherion fired... So why am I still alive?

104
00:09:45,020 --> 00:09:48,190
Finally... Finally, the time has come!

105
00:09:49,010 --> 00:09:50,110
Why, you...

106
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:53,760
This is the true form of the Tower of Heaven!

107
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:55,960
It's a giant lacrima!

108
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:58,530
And thanks to the attack
by the Council's Etherion,

109
00:09:58,530 --> 00:10:02,650
it has absorbed an incredible
amount of magical energy!

110
00:10:02,650 --> 00:10:05,760
Now the R-system is complete!

111
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:10,230
The target is standing!

112
00:10:10,230 --> 00:10:11,540
A giant lacrima!

113
00:10:11,540 --> 00:10:15,420
The lacrima absorbed the 
magical power from Etherion!

114
00:10:15,420 --> 00:10:16,960
It what?!

115
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:23,190
Sieg... What is the meaning of this?

116
00:10:27,340 --> 00:10:28,870
He disappeared...

117
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,490
You tricked me?

118
00:10:45,380 --> 00:10:47,160
You were really cute there, Erza.

119
00:10:48,930 --> 00:10:52,570
Jellal was not able to produce his true power.

120
00:10:52,570 --> 00:10:55,380
He was in mortal danger, so he 
had no choice but to trick you.

121
00:10:56,390 --> 00:10:57,760
Siegrain!

122
00:11:12,760 --> 00:11:15,460
Why are you here?

123
00:11:15,460 --> 00:11:19,980
Remember the first time we met, Erza.

124
00:11:21,790 --> 00:11:27,450
That time you came with Makarov to deliver a 
written letter of apology to the council, yes?

125
00:11:27,450 --> 00:11:31,210
You mistook me for Jellal and attacked me.

126
00:11:31,210 --> 00:11:34,620
Well, we look identical, so it's to be expected.

127
00:11:35,470 --> 00:11:39,050
After you heard we were twins, 
you finally were pacified.

128
00:11:39,050 --> 00:11:42,620
However you always treated me as your enemy.

129
00:11:42,620 --> 00:11:43,980
Obviously!

130
00:11:43,980 --> 00:11:48,200
Instead of behaving as an older brother 
should, you tolerated what Jellal was doing!

131
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:51,430
Or rather, you were spying on me!

132
00:11:51,430 --> 00:11:52,800
Yes.

133
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:54,950
That was my mistake.

134
00:11:54,950 --> 00:12:00,880
I should have said something like "I will find 
Jellal and make him stop, no matter what."

135
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:03,500
I had finally become a member of the council,

136
00:12:03,500 --> 00:12:06,670
so meeting you at all was my greatest mistake.

137
00:12:07,110 --> 00:12:10,430
The lies we tell in an unplanned 
moment cause us the greatest pain.

138
00:12:11,100 --> 00:12:15,210
So you two really did plot this together.

139
00:12:15,210 --> 00:12:16,750
Together?

140
00:12:16,750 --> 00:12:17,810
No.

141
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:21,070
That's not it, Erza.

142
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:26,270
We are a single person.

143
00:12:26,270 --> 00:12:27,960
From the very beginning.

144
00:12:38,340 --> 00:12:39,710
No...

145
00:12:40,140 --> 00:12:41,650
A thought projection?

146
00:12:42,290 --> 00:12:45,610
Yes. Siegrain is me.

147
00:12:45,610 --> 00:12:49,140
So you, yourself, fired Etherion?

148
00:12:49,140 --> 00:12:51,580
That's why you infiltrated the Council?

149
00:12:51,870 --> 00:12:55,540
Did you enjoy your fleeting freedom, Erza?

150
00:12:55,540 --> 00:12:59,540
Everything went according to 
Zeref's scenario for resurrection.

151
00:13:00,090 --> 00:13:04,340
You fiend... How many people 
have you deceived in your life?

152
00:13:05,430 --> 00:13:06,800
Power...

153
00:13:08,340 --> 00:13:10,810
...my magical power has returned!

154
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:14,260
A tremendous magical power is 
building in the Tower of Heaven!

155
00:13:14,260 --> 00:13:17,470
If that magical power is held 
in one place it'll explode!

156
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:19,270
We were had.

157
00:13:22,030 --> 00:13:24,110
What is going on?

158
00:13:24,110 --> 00:13:27,110
The building is suddenly aging!

159
00:13:27,110 --> 00:13:29,130
Lost Magic?

160
00:13:29,130 --> 00:13:30,780
Time Ark?

161
00:13:42,540 --> 00:13:44,090
Ultear...

162
00:13:44,510 --> 00:13:49,920
Everything is for Lord 
Sieg... I mean, Lord Jellal.

163
00:13:50,690 --> 00:13:55,520
Right now, his dream is being fulfilled!

164
00:13:56,180 --> 00:13:59,270
That's the R-system?

165
00:13:59,270 --> 00:14:04,660
Yes, that's the true form of 
the R-system we built, got it?

166
00:14:05,220 --> 00:14:07,120
It's activating...

167
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:10,450
Activating? You mean it's resurrecting Zeref?

168
00:14:10,730 --> 00:14:15,700
I don't know. We've never seen it operate.

169
00:14:15,700 --> 00:14:18,290
And Natsu and Erza are inside of it?

170
00:14:18,570 --> 00:14:22,050
Simon as well... And, Jellal...

171
00:14:26,640 --> 00:14:29,460
What happened to your previous strength?

172
00:14:29,460 --> 00:14:33,670
Did you use up too much of your magical 
power in the battle with Ikaruga?

173
00:14:36,350 --> 00:14:38,640
Jellal!

174
00:14:45,730 --> 00:14:49,890
Right now the Council should 
be completely paralyzed.

175
00:14:50,370 --> 00:14:52,620
I must be grateful to Ultear.

176
00:14:53,540 --> 00:14:55,670
She did quite well.

177
00:14:55,670 --> 00:15:00,830
She said, "If in heaven all are seen as 
one, then we need not fear even death."

178
00:15:01,510 --> 00:15:08,110
For my ideal, for my dream, she said 
she'd gladly lay down her own life.

179
00:15:09,590 --> 00:15:15,110
I truly must be thankful 
to be given stupid women!

180
00:15:15,110 --> 00:15:16,650
You fiend!

181
00:15:18,660 --> 00:15:23,940
You should die from the curses 
of all those you've used!

182
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:28,150
What is this?

183
00:15:28,150 --> 00:15:30,210
Bind Snake.

184
00:15:30,210 --> 00:15:33,200
I put it on you when we hugged before.

185
00:15:37,090 --> 00:15:41,060
I have the magical power 
to activate the R-system.

186
00:15:41,060 --> 00:15:44,690
All I need now is the human 
sacrifice to resurrect Zeref.

187
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:50,550
I have no more time to play with you, Erza.

188
00:15:51,460 --> 00:15:54,610
The tremendous amount of magical 
power this lacrima now stores,

189
00:15:54,610 --> 00:15:57,050
will be fused into your body.

190
00:15:57,050 --> 00:16:03,060
Your body will be deconstructed, 
and then reconstituted into Zeref's.

191
00:16:11,780 --> 00:16:14,950
I loved you, Erza.

192
00:16:14,950 --> 00:16:17,910
Damn it! Damn!

193
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:25,250
O Great Zeref...

194
00:16:26,130 --> 00:16:30,250
I give to you this woman's body!

195
00:16:34,160 --> 00:16:35,880
Jellal!

196
00:16:38,140 --> 00:16:39,850
Jellal!

197
00:16:42,930 --> 00:16:44,630
Gotcha.

198
00:16:48,490 --> 00:16:51,360
Erza is a Fairy Tail wizard.

199
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:53,350
You can't have her.

200
00:16:57,950 --> 00:16:58,910
Natsu...

201
00:17:00,880 --> 00:17:01,740
Sheesh.

202
00:17:02,380 --> 00:17:04,220
What are you doing?

203
00:17:04,220 --> 00:17:08,410
We need to get back and do some work, 
or the rent won't get paid this month.

204
00:17:08,410 --> 00:17:09,370
Lucy's rent, that is.

205
00:17:09,370 --> 00:17:12,500
Sorry. I can't move.

206
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:13,810
Oh, yeah?

207
00:17:14,780 --> 00:17:16,970
You used to work me over pretty good!

208
00:17:16,970 --> 00:17:18,440
So take some of this!

209
00:17:20,800 --> 00:17:24,160
Natsu, get away from here as soon as you can.

210
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:25,460
Not a chance.

211
00:17:25,460 --> 00:17:28,100
If you can't do it, then I'll do it for you.

212
00:17:28,730 --> 00:17:31,160
Stop. He's got the advantage.

213
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:33,560
You don't know enough about him.

214
00:17:33,560 --> 00:17:35,650
So I can't win unless I do?

215
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:39,780
Please, listen to me.

216
00:17:43,830 --> 00:17:44,920
What are you...

217
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:47,770
Erza, I don't know anything about you either.

218
00:17:48,330 --> 00:17:50,380
But... I can win!

219
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:59,660
You're even more outrageous than the rumors say.

220
00:18:00,020 --> 00:18:04,010
Had enough of hurting your 
friend when she can't move?

221
00:18:04,530 --> 00:18:05,720
Erza...

222
00:18:08,600 --> 00:18:09,580
...was crying.

223
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:14,580
She was giving up...

224
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:18,450
And her voice was shaking...

225
00:18:19,550 --> 00:18:21,920
I don't want to see Erza like that.

226
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:24,680
Erza should be strong and ferocious!

227
00:18:26,390 --> 00:18:31,480
I want her to be her usual self when 
she wakes up from this nightmare.

228
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:36,170
I will fight!

229
00:18:36,840 --> 00:18:43,040
Interesting! Show me the dragon wizard's power!

230
00:18:56,730 --> 00:18:58,570
Wing Slash of the Fire Dragon!

231
00:19:00,640 --> 00:19:01,680
And!

232
00:19:01,680 --> 00:19:02,700
Talons!

233
00:19:03,930 --> 00:19:06,950
Roar of the Fire Dragon!

234
00:19:24,580 --> 00:19:26,220
Are you being serious?

235
00:19:29,710 --> 00:19:33,590
Natsu Dragneel... The child of Igneel.

236
00:19:35,450 --> 00:19:42,780
I wanted to taste the destructive power 
of a Dragon Slayer before I destroyed you,

237
00:19:42,780 --> 00:19:45,410
but this is nothing to fear at all.

238
00:19:45,410 --> 00:19:47,370
Say what?!

239
00:19:47,370 --> 00:19:50,560
How dare you interrupt the ceremony...

240
00:19:50,560 --> 00:19:53,910
I will use my Heavenly Body 
Magic to tear you to shreds!

241
00:19:53,910 --> 00:19:54,960
Meteor!

242
00:20:04,250 --> 00:20:06,090
Damn it! He's too fast!

243
00:20:06,850 --> 00:20:09,350
I shouldn't follow him with my eyes!

244
00:20:10,220 --> 00:20:13,390
Smell, sound, feel...

245
00:20:13,390 --> 00:20:15,730
Predict his movements... Concentrate...

246
00:20:15,730 --> 00:20:16,350
Concentrate!

247
00:20:18,580 --> 00:20:20,190
There!

248
00:20:21,840 --> 00:20:23,450
He's even faster?

249
00:20:25,890 --> 00:20:29,430
Your attacks will never hit me again!

250
00:20:37,630 --> 00:20:42,840
This is the end. I will show 
you true destructive magic.

251
00:20:45,630 --> 00:20:48,130
Be judged under the seven stars!

252
00:20:48,630 --> 00:20:50,580
Seven Star Blades!

253
00:20:50,580 --> 00:20:52,640
Grand Chariot!

254
00:21:03,320 --> 00:21:08,030
That's a spell that destroys 
with the power of falling meteors.

255
00:21:08,030 --> 00:21:10,830
I'm impressed your body is still intact.

256
00:21:11,240 --> 00:21:13,690
Perhaps I went a bit overboard.

257
00:21:13,990 --> 00:21:18,200
It would be dangerous to damage 
the R-system any further.

258
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:20,840
The magical power is starting to leak out.

259
00:21:22,730 --> 00:21:24,070
I must hurry.

260
00:21:27,060 --> 00:21:28,840
Isn't that right, Erza?

261
00:21:50,980 --> 00:21:53,120
That attack hit.

262
00:21:53,120 --> 00:21:58,440
So breaking this tower, or um, 
lacrima... That's bad, huh?

263
00:22:00,580 --> 00:22:02,880
Rotten luck for you!

264
00:22:03,330 --> 00:22:04,610
Don't!

265
00:22:06,380 --> 00:22:10,550
Breaking things happens to be 
Fairy Tail wizards' specialty!

266
00:22:11,540 --> 00:22:15,470
I'm all fired up! More than I've ever been!

267
00:22:17,490 --> 00:22:19,980
You little brat!

268
00:23:56,160 --> 00:23:59,120
Natsu, Etherion has started 
going out of control!

269
00:23:59,120 --> 00:24:00,830
At this rate everyone will be destroyed!

270
00:24:01,160 --> 00:24:03,080
Damn it! There must be a way!

271
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:05,790
Erza, what are you doing?

272
00:24:06,110 --> 00:24:07,530
Throwing your body into the lacrima?

273
00:24:07,530 --> 00:24:11,530
Is she attempting to fuse with Etherion 
and stop it from going out of control?

274
00:24:11,530 --> 00:24:13,880
Stop it!

275
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:16,890
Next time: Titania Falls

276
00:24:16,890 --> 00:24:18,850
Erza disappeared...

277
00:24:18,850 --> 00:24:21,980
I won't accept it! I won't accept it, damn it!

278
00:24:21,980 --> 00:24:24,440
Erza!

279
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:26,690


